---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Stack from "../../components/organisms/Stack.astro";
---

<Layout>
    <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-zinc-200">About me</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 mb-10">
            <p>
                Hello, I'm Jack. I am a self-taught software developer and technical writer from the UK. I enjoy
                building software, and writing about how it works. 
            </p>
            <p>Some of the things I've done professionally:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-8">
                <li>
                    Built production web applications
                </li>
                <li>Collaborated with designers, developers, and animators</li>
                <li>
                    Maintained open source developer documentation
                </li>
                <li>Created tutorials for TypeScript SDKs</li>
                <li>Built Telegram bots</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                I am a dedicated developer and technical writer, and take a
                passionate and pragmatic approach to my work.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-8">Technologies</h3>
            <Stack />
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
